# MUI theme contract (exact)

## Required light palette (must match exactly)
- `palette.mode`: `"light"`
- `palette.primary.main`: `#111111`
- `palette.secondary.main`: `#f3e8e3`
- `palette.background.default`: `#f6f1ee`
- `palette.background.paper`: `#ffffff`
- `palette.text.primary`: `#111111`
- `palette.text.secondary`: `#666666`

## Required dark palette (design-consistent)
- Must provide a dark palette where:
  - `background.default` and `background.paper` are dark surfaces
  - `text.primary` is high-contrast (near-white)
  - `text.secondary` is muted (gray)
  - Components remain readable with `CssBaseline`

## Typography (required)
- `typography.fontFamily`: `"'Inter', 'Poppins', 'Assistant', 'Heebo', sans-serif"`
- `typography.h1`: `36px / 700 / lineHeight 1.2`
- `typography.body1`: `16px` and uses muted text tone (do not hardcode hex in components)
- `typography.button`: `textTransform: "none"`, `fontWeight: 500`

## Shape (required)
- `shape.borderRadius`: `16`

## Shadows (required)
- Set `shadows[1]` to soft shadow:
  - Light: `0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05)`
  - Dark: may be stronger but must remain soft (no harsh outlines)

## Direction (required)
- `direction: 'rtl'`

